1a:T476,Internal evidence clearly defines this as a comprehensive reagent collection for the AutoQuant 400 Supremus analyzer with 25+ test parameters covering proteins, enzymes, lipids, electrolytes, and specialized markers. External evidence confirms Meril Life Sciences manufactures diagnostic products including analyzers and reagents, but does not provide specific verification of the AutoQuant 400 reagent line. The product structure (liquid reagents, specific bottle sizes, refrigerated storage, analyzer compatibility) is consistent with clinical chemistry reagent systems. Brand field is empty which requires review. The entity is appropriately classified as a reagent_line rather than individual reagents. Recommended for review due to: (1) missing brand confirmation in internal data, (2) lack of external source specifically mentioning AutoQuant 400 reagent collection, (3) need to verify whether this should be split into individual reagent products or maintained as a collection page. High confidence in the clinical function and scope based on comprehensive internal specification, but organizational structure needs human verification.16:["$","$L19",null,{"product":{"product_name":"AutoQuant 400 Biochemistry Reagent Kit Collection","product_name_display":"Biochemistry Reagent Kit Collection","sku_code":"AQ4-REG-001","product_family":"AutoQuant 400 Biochemistry Reagent Kit Collection","product_family_display":"AutoQuant 400 Biochemistry Reagent Kit Collection","slug":"autoquant-400-biochemistry-reagent-kit-collection","images":[{"id":"prop_69c41e7","storage_path":"agile-ortho/products/69c3dee36be1486691088284/cover_feabf07c.jpg","original_filename":"cover_Quantilyte_Brochure.pdf.jpg","content_type":"image/jpeg","size":424703,"uploaded_at":"2026-03-26T05:58:21.280251+00:00","source":"family_propagation","width":1654,"height":2339}],"status":"published","live_visible":true,"brochure_url":"","seo_meta_title":"Biochemistry Reagent Kit Collection | AutoQuant 400 Biochemistry